Class ChangePromptComponents

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codename1.ui.Component

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.codename1.ui.animations.Animation, com.codename1.ui.Editable, com.codename1.ui.events.StyleListener, java.lang.Iterable<com.codename1.ui.Component>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CreatePromptPage, EditPromptPage
    class ChangePromptComponents
extends DefaultPageComponents
    A parent class for creating/changing a prompt. Meant to be extended. Child class of DefaultPageComponents. Adds to this by creating the components needed to edit/create a prompt. setTextAreas() must be called if editing an existing prompt
